{"lemma":"مَفْزَعٌ","slug":"مَفْزَعٌ","root":"ف.ز.ع","root_slug":"ف-ز-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ز-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33809"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%92%D8%B2%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"terrifying, frightening, horrifying, appalling, dreadful"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"shelter, refuge, recourse, sanctuary"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of أَفْزَعَ (ʔafzaʕa, “to frighten”).\n\nNoun of place from the root ف ز ع (f z ʕ)."},"ipa":["/muf.ziʕ/","/maf.zaʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33809","headword_ar":"مَفْزَعٌ","root":"fzE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malojaA^o","text_ar":"مَلْجَاْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A refuge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place to which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a person to whom, one betakes himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has recourse, for refuge, protection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preservation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, O, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the occasion of the befalling of an affliction"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a calamity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) applied to a sing. and a pl. (S, O, K) and a dual (S, O) and a masc. and a fem.; (S, O, K;) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN mafozaEN liln~aAsi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ مَفْزَعٌ لِلنَّاسِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is a refuge to men when an event comes upon them suddenly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humaAmafozaEN liln~aAsi","text_ar":"هُمَامَفْزَعٌ لِلنَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo mafozaEN","text_ar":"هُمْ مَفْزَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.; (S, O;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafozaEapN","text_ar":"مَفْزَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the same in signification and in its applications; (K;) expl. by IF as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place to which one who is in fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frightened, betakes himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has recourse, for refuge, protection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preservation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafozaEN","text_ar":"مَفْزَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies one of whom aid, or succour, is sought, or demanded: (K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafozaEapN","text_ar":"مَفْزَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cause of fear"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fright;"},{"kind":"text","text":"being a word of the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maboxalapN","text_ar":"مَبْخَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majobanapN","text_ar":"مَجْبَنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that one is made to fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at which one is frightened;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a person whom one is made to fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at whom one is frightened;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuzoEapN","text_ar":"فُزْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on account of whom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the sake of whom, one is made to fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is frightened:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, K:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN lanaA mafozaEapN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَنَا مَفْزَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is to us a person whom we are made to fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], and in like manner you say of a female, and of a pl. number. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA","Lth"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}